{"title":"给一位将军（外一章）","authors":["田间"],"dates":[{"year":1954,"month":3,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位将军（外一章）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位将军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当敌人炮轰板门店，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"板门店烟雾弥漫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"板门店和平的帐篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帐篷上也溅着血斑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你底手拦住大炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你底话胜过炸弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——人民军志愿军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和你一同呐喊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"板门店和平的帐篷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屹立着如一座高山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大将和人民一个步伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨进和平的门槛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们和平的步伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经把世界震撼："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——不准大炮叫嚣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要让和平呐喊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五三年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十日作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给一位母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松谷里的山上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站着一位母亲；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在早晨，在黄昏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她在望着北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我知道：在北京"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也有她的亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当她想起亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她就想起北京。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我记得阿妈妮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她说过这样的话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要到中国来看看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要带一朵好的花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我也问过和平使者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的家现在在哪？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她的家是不是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还在那三棵栗树下？〔注〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一条砂川河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流过栗树旁边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阿妈妮和志愿军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喝过那儿的清泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中朝人民的血迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还留在砂川河边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们曾经在栗子树下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一同和侵略者作过战。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听说阿妈妮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常常站在山上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她抬起她的脸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远地望着北方——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在北方有什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有和平的家乡；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平的男女们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隔着江一同歌唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五四年春天作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕这是美李匪帮谋杀和平战士姚庆祥排长的地方。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}